00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:16.860
Chicago Was Once Raised 6 Feet (and no-one
noticed)

00:00:16.860 --> 00:00:20.780
There are some facts that you instinctively
know are BS, even if you’re not sure why.

00:00:20.780 --> 00:00:25.250
The idea that someone once managed to make
the city of Chicago levitate 6 feet in the

00:00:25.250 --> 00:00:28.680
air without anyone noticing is definitely
one such fact.

00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:30.210
For one thing, it’s impossible.

00:00:30.210 --> 00:00:32.940
For another, well, just listen to what you’re
saying.

00:00:32.940 --> 00:00:35.680
You might as well claim the Moon is made of
cheese.

00:00:35.680 --> 00:00:40.640
Well, sorry, but we’re about to completely
mess with your perception of how reality works.

00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:45.479
On New Year’s Eve 1855, the Chicago Board
of Sewage Commissioners tasked engineer E.S.

00:00:45.479 --> 00:00:49.530
Chesbrough with finding a solution to the
city’s regular cholera outbreaks.

00:00:49.530 --> 00:00:54.030
Chesbrough decided the easiest option would
be to hike the entire city out its swamp,

00:00:54.030 --> 00:00:55.799
6 feet into the air.

00:00:55.799 --> 00:00:59.539
It was known as the Raising of Chicago, and
it was completely literal.

00:00:59.539 --> 00:01:04.049
To get the city out the cholera-infested swamp
it sat on, hundreds of men jacked up the streets

00:01:04.049 --> 00:01:08.810
using massive screws, filled in the space
beneath them, and called the result ‘ground

00:01:08.810 --> 00:01:09.810
level’.

00:01:09.810 --> 00:01:12.450
The work carried on for 20 years, and was
often completely mad.

00:01:12.450 --> 00:01:17.420
There are stories of whole hotels being hoisted
up into the air, and not a single person inside

00:01:17.420 --> 00:01:19.340
them realizing it was happening.

00:01:19.340 --> 00:01:20.500
Nor was it a temporary fix.

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:22.909
The Chicago you see today is the ‘raised’
version.

00:01:22.909 --> 00:01:28.840
That’s right: Chicago is still levitating
today, and no-one living there has ever noticed.

00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:29.840
