00:04:59.080 --> 00:05:01.880
We Still Have No Idea How Many People Chernobyl
Killed

00:05:01.880 --> 00:05:06.420
On April 26, 1986, the nuclear reactor at
Chernobyl, Ukraine, exploded.

00:05:06.420 --> 00:05:11.420
The resulting meltdown killed 31 people more-or-less
instantly, and poisoned millions of square

00:05:11.420 --> 00:05:12.950
miles of land.

00:05:12.950 --> 00:05:17.120
At the time, the World Health Organization
estimated the disaster would ultimately cause

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:19.810
4,000 deaths from radiation-induced cancer.

00:05:19.810 --> 00:05:22.139
Over 30 years later, we’re still guessing.

00:05:22.139 --> 00:05:26.300
Depending on your source, Chernobyl caused
anywhere from a mere 53 deaths, to over half

00:05:26.300 --> 00:05:27.300
a million.

00:05:27.300 --> 00:05:31.560
The trouble is Chernobyl blew radiation over
such a vast area, no one really knows how

00:05:31.560 --> 00:05:35.630
many excess fatal cancers in Europe, Asia
and Africa are due to the accident.

00:05:35.630 --> 00:05:38.100
The UN estimates around 16,000.

00:05:38.100 --> 00:05:40.960
The Russian Academy of Sciences estimates
up to 200,000.

00:05:40.960 --> 00:05:45.930
The Ukraine National Commission for Radiation
Protection calculates 500,000.

00:05:45.930 --> 00:05:47.790
And those numbers keep climbing.

00:05:47.790 --> 00:05:51.980
One recent high-end estimate pegged the total
number dead at nearly one million.

00:05:51.980 --> 00:05:57.080
If true, that would make Chernobyl the deadliest
disaster in human history bar the catastrophic

00:05:57.080 --> 00:06:01.669
China Floods of 1931 (which may have killed
up to 4 million).

00:06:01.669 --> 00:06:05.900
For comparison, the combined atomic bombing
of Nagasaki and Hiroshima killed a maximum

00:06:05.900 --> 00:06:07.010
of 236,000.

00:06:07.010 --> 00:06:12.150
That’s right, the screw up of a bunch of
Soviet engineers may yet turn out to be deadlier

00:06:12.150 --> 00:06:16.390
than the bloody endgame of the most-brutal
war in human history.

00:06:16.390 --> 00:06:17.390
